  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Idle puzzle in the style of electrical circuits. Change the positions of the wires to increase your income. You'll need to connect pluses with minuses, as well as various cells in the most efficient way to earn as much as possible. You'll encounter a standard square grid, a hexagonal grid, and an octagonal grid. Buy upgrades in the shop to develop your circuit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on the laws of physics.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Idle puzzle in the style of electrical circuits. Change the positions of the wires to increase your income. You'll need to connect pluses with minuses, as well as various cells in the most efficient way to earn as much as possible. You'll encounter a standard square grid, a hexagonal grid, and an octagonal grid. Buy upgrades in the shop to develop your circuit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on the laws of physics.</p>",
